WEBVTT

00:00.005 --> 00:01.979
Previously on
"Devious Maids"...

00:02.013 --> 00:04.197
We can prove Flora Hernandez
found out she was pregnant

00:04.215 --> 00:05.865
just before she was murdered,

00:05.883 --> 00:07.500
- and my client wasn't the father.
- Mom, it's me.

00:07.534 --> 00:08.885
I remembered something.

00:08.919 --> 00:10.253
Of course he will pay,

00:10.304 --> 00:11.554
because it's on video.

00:11.589 --> 00:14.174
We need to find a way to stay together
for Tucker's sake.

00:14.208 --> 00:16.142
And if that means changing
the rules of our relationship,

00:16.177 --> 00:17.343
I'm willing to consider it.

00:17.377 --> 00:19.562
Last night Spence told me

00:19.597 --> 00:21.231
he was willing
to have an open marriage.

00:21.265 --> 00:23.266
When a man starts talking
about having an open marriage,

00:23.317 --> 00:25.518
it's not because he wants
his wife to have a good time.

00:25.552 --> 00:27.220
Your husband's having
an affair.

00:27.238 --> 00:28.488
Do you see that man out there?

00:28.522 --> 00:30.406
- Yeah. Who is he?
- My husband.

00:30.441 --> 00:32.442
- You're going with me.
- No, I'm not.

00:32.493 --> 00:35.111
Oscar, no! Aah!

00:36.330 --> 00:37.447
I saw the way you fought
for me, Sam,

00:37.498 --> 00:39.082
but the thing is...

00:39.116 --> 00:41.534
- You don't want a relationship.
- No.

00:41.568 --> 00:43.203
What kind of fun
did you have in mind?

00:43.237 --> 00:46.122
I... haven't done that
in a while.

00:46.173 --> 00:48.124
You owe me.

00:48.175 --> 00:50.093
This new therapist is a genius.

00:50.127 --> 00:52.578
He could tell that I needed
to be on mood stabilizers

00:52.596 --> 00:55.181
within five minutes
of meeting me.

00:55.216 --> 00:57.016
It took him that long?

