17:34.363 --> 17:35.830
I need you.

17:35.864 --> 17:38.583
What you need is
a big dose of reality.

17:38.617 --> 17:40.702
Your life has changed.

17:40.753 --> 17:42.954
You gotta start being smart.

17:42.988 --> 17:46.657
If I can think of a way out
of this mess, will you stay?

17:46.675 --> 17:47.875
I suppose.

17:47.926 --> 17:49.877
Okay. Okay.

17:49.928 --> 17:51.796
You just watch.

17:51.830 --> 17:53.931
I'm about to be smart.

17:53.966 --> 17:55.466
So...

17:55.500 --> 17:58.019
The question is,
how can I make some money?

17:58.053 --> 18:00.138
You could get a job.

18:00.172 --> 18:02.840
Honey, this is serious.
Don't make jokes.

18:02.858 --> 18:04.809
Sorry.

18:04.843 --> 18:06.343
Hey!

18:06.361 --> 18:08.780
Why don't I just get someone
to give me the money?

18:08.814 --> 18:10.681
