asking them for money.

18:13.869 --> 18:15.453
You're right.

18:15.487 --> 18:19.741
I have to borrow from someone
who really loves me.

18:21.827 --> 18:25.630
Someone like
a rich ex-husband...

18:25.664 --> 18:27.999
