about the way he treated you.

18:28.033 --> 18:30.001
Oh, Zoila!

18:30.035 --> 18:32.887
I like being smart.

18:38.074 --> 18:39.575
Carmen?

18:39.609 --> 18:42.077
Hey. What are you doing
out here?

18:42.111 --> 18:43.579
Thought you might want
a smoothie.

18:43.613 --> 18:45.948
Ah. After 6 miles?

18:45.982 --> 18:47.282
You bet.

18:47.316 --> 18:48.700
Mmm. While you're
catching your breath,

18:48.751 --> 18:50.369
can I talk to you
about something?

18:50.420 --> 18:52.421
Sure.

18:52.455 --> 18:54.423
One of your employees

18:54.457 --> 18:56.121
had sex last night...

18:56.156 --> 18:57.960
in your house...

18:57.994 --> 18:59.160
with a woman.

19:00.463 --> 19:02.297
No, no, no, no.
It wasn't me.

19:02.331 --> 19:03.548
You can put that eyebrow down.

19:03.600 --> 19:05.550
So Sam got laid.

19:05.602 --> 19:07.519
- Mm-hmm.
- Ah! Good for him.

19:07.553 --> 19:09.771
No! No! Not good.

19:09.806 --> 19:11.356
This woman that
came into your house...

19:11.391 --> 19:13.174
she's not all there.

19:14.277 --> 19:16.979
She's bald?

19:17.013 --> 19:18.113
No, she's crazy.

19:18.147 --> 19:20.065
- Really?
- Yeah. I met her.

19:20.116 --> 19:22.618
Psychotic. Or on drugs.
Or both.

19:22.652 --> 19:23.986
Either way, I think
you should tell Sam

19:24.020 --> 19:26.021
that he can't bring her
into your house.

19:26.039 --> 19:28.657
Let me tell you
a little something about Sam.

19:28.691 --> 19:30.575
He's been working here
for four years.

19:30.627 --> 19:32.027
He's been lonely
the whole time.

19:32.045 --> 19:34.529
And I'm thrilled
he's finally found someone.

19:34.547 --> 19:37.165
We should be happy for him,
not, uh...

19:37.199 --> 19:38.800
meddling in his love life.

19:38.835 --> 19:41.219
No, I-I don't care about
his love life.

19:42.505 --> 19:44.973
I just want him
to respect your house.

19:45.008 --> 19:47.142
Well, thank you very much,

19:47.176 --> 19:50.729
but I'm sure the house can
survive a booty call or two.

19:52.048 --> 19:53.348
Hi, Alejandro.

19:53.382 --> 19:55.267
Hey, Mrs. Crump.

19:57.186 --> 19:59.154
Um... excuse me?

19:59.188 --> 20:00.605
You're Mrs. Crump?

20:00.657 --> 20:02.357
Yes.
You live over on canon?

20:02.391 --> 20:04.225
Yes, I do.

20:04.243 --> 20:05.494
I'm Carmen.

20:05.528 --> 20:07.162
I work for Alejandro.

20:07.196 --> 20:08.563
Oh.

20:08.581 --> 20:12.167
I have to say, that is
one beautiful rottweiler.

20:12.201 --> 20:13.368
Why, thank you.

20:13.402 --> 20:15.587
I just love dogs.

20:15.621 --> 20:18.206
If you ever need anyone
to walk him,

20:18.240 --> 20:19.758
I'd be happy to.

20:29.552 --> 20:30.602
He's ready to see you now.

20:30.636 --> 20:32.604
Will you come this way?

20:51.440 --> 20:53.375
Mrs. Delatour.

20:53.409 --> 20:56.328
Mr. Delatour.

20:56.379 --> 20:58.630
How are you?

20:58.664 --> 21:00.448
How's our son?

21:00.466 --> 21:02.634
Remi is wonderful.

21:02.668 --> 21:05.170
You don't call him
as much as you should.

21:05.221 --> 21:06.588
You're right.
You're absolutely right.

21:09.342 --> 21:11.810
My God,

21:11.844 --> 21:14.346
you're as devastatingly
beautiful as ever.

21:14.397 --> 21:16.732
Why in the world
did we ever divorce?

21:16.766 --> 21:19.351
You kept committing adultery.

21:19.402 --> 21:21.069
Oh, that's right.

21:21.104 --> 21:22.988
You must have been
so disappointed in me.

21:23.022 --> 21:26.307
