when I married you.

21:26.325 --> 21:29.745
Yeah, still, I regret sleeping
with so many of your friends.

21:29.779 --> 21:32.364
I was able to get new friends.

21:32.415 --> 21:34.533
And then I slept
with your sister.

21:34.584 --> 21:38.370
Yes. Well, that was
a bit more awkward.

21:38.421 --> 21:40.505
Philippe...

21:40.540 --> 21:42.507
If time has taught me anything,

21:42.542 --> 21:45.260
it's how to forgive,

21:45.294 --> 21:47.796
- so consider yourself forgiven.
- Oh.

21:47.830 --> 21:49.998
I want us to be friends again.

21:51.467 --> 21:53.185
This wouldn't have
anything to do

21:53.219 --> 21:56.354
