24:46.642 --> 24:47.943
Where's Peri?

24:47.977 --> 24:50.946
She left for a costume fitting.

24:50.980 --> 24:52.280
Oh?

24:54.516 --> 24:56.651
Good.

24:56.685 --> 24:58.820
- Mmm.
- What are you doing?

24:58.854 --> 25:00.739
I must not be doing it well
if you have to ask.

25:00.790 --> 25:02.490
No. Mrs. Peri will
be back soon.

25:02.524 --> 25:04.409
So?

25:04.460 --> 25:06.911
So if I don't get my work done,
she is going to fire me.

25:06.963 --> 25:09.748
But I need to be with you.

25:13.052 --> 25:14.836
- Okay.
- Mmm.

25:14.870 --> 25:16.504
But we have to do it fast.

25:16.538 --> 25:17.922
Mrs. Peri told me
to fix the toilet in the den

25:17.974 --> 25:19.541
before she gets back.

25:19.575 --> 25:22.060
I'll have you holding
that plunger in no time.

25:24.046 --> 25:26.231
- Mmm. Thank you, Mr. Spence.
- Mmm.

25:26.265 --> 25:29.050
Ooh, just Spence.
