what the doctors said.

26:51.118 --> 26:54.004
I don't understand. What was
he doing when this happened?

26:54.055 --> 26:56.056
Huh?

26:56.090 --> 26:58.925
I mean, was he exercising?

26:58.959 --> 27:01.961
Yes. I'd say so.

27:01.979 --> 27:03.063
Mm-hmm.

27:03.097 --> 27:04.347
Mrs. Westmore?

27:04.398 --> 27:05.932
I'm Dr. Kagan.

27:05.966 --> 27:07.184
I wanna talk to you about
your husband's condition.

27:07.235 --> 27:09.236
Is he gonna die?

27:09.270 --> 27:12.189
No, no. He's in intensive care,
but he's stable.

27:12.240 --> 27:13.773
Thank God.

27:13.807 --> 27:15.075
I need to see him.

27:15.109 --> 27:17.777
Sure.
Uh, just for a moment.

27:17.811 --> 27:19.479
Can I see him, too?

27:20.781 --> 27:22.165
I'm sorry. You are...

27:22.200 --> 27:24.367
This is Rosie, our maid.

27:24.418 --> 27:27.954
