27:50.444 --> 27:53.780
<i>Mi casa es su casa.</i>

27:56.117 --> 27:57.850
Thank you.

28:21.375 --> 28:24.344
Did you find your... key?

28:24.378 --> 28:27.380
Nope.

28:27.398 --> 28:29.215
Must have left it
somewhere else.

28:29.233 --> 28:32.319
Good luck finding it.

28:50.338 --> 28:52.339
Hmm.

28:57.428 --> 29:00.347
Okay, let's go.

29:01.432 --> 29:03.416
Come on, buddy. Come on.

29:03.434 --> 29:05.385
Come here. Come here.

29:05.419 --> 29:07.470
Find the treat.

29:07.521 --> 29:11.057
It's so delicious, right?
So delicious.

29:11.091 --> 29:12.925
Good boy! Good boy!

29:12.943 --> 29:16.896
