be allergic to you?

29:16.930 --> 29:19.199
Okay, let's go.

29:19.233 --> 29:21.117
Come on, come on, come on.

29:25.956 --> 29:27.073
Yeah?

29:44.258 --> 29:46.393
Baby, I swear
we don't have a dog!

29:46.427 --> 29:48.061
You must have!

29:48.095 --> 29:51.130
It's the only thing
I'm allergic to!

30:04.245 --> 30:06.029
What's that?

30:06.080 --> 30:07.614
It's dog fur,

30:07.648 --> 30:08.948
and it's all over my sheets,

30:08.982 --> 30:10.750
along with crumbs
from a dog biscuit.

30:10.785 --> 30:12.535
Well, whatever kinky stuff
you and Julie are into,

30:12.586 --> 30:14.371
that's your business.

30:14.422 --> 30:18.041
Carmen, this is really
how you're gonna be right now?

30:19.427 --> 30:21.177
Okay!

30:21.212 --> 30:22.545
I did it.

30:22.596 --> 30:23.463
But I just thought she was
gonna get, like, a...

30:23.497 --> 30:25.131
like a rash or something.

30:25.165 --> 30:26.433
You could've killed her.
I know.

30:26.467 --> 30:28.385
I'm sorry.

30:28.436 --> 30:30.303
I just wanted her to go away.

30:30.337 --> 30:32.105
Are you jealous?

30:32.139 --> 30:34.307
No.

30:34.341 --> 30:35.675
Are you sure?

30:35.693 --> 30:37.394
I don't know what I was
feeling or... or thinking.

30:37.445 --> 30:39.612
I'm just... I'm sorry.

30:39.647 --> 30:42.348
I-I am very, very sorry.

30:42.366 --> 30:46.152
You had your chance.
You turned me down.

30:46.186 --> 30:47.704
So if you're not gonna
be with me,

30:47.738 --> 30:49.622
you have to let me be
with someone else.

30:49.657 --> 30:51.541
Okay?

31:06.557 --> 31:08.591
I told you to sell this.

31:08.642 --> 31:10.643
No.
I want you to have it.

31:10.678 --> 31:12.929
- Genevieve, I...
- Listen to me.

31:12.980 --> 31:15.432
I've had
six different husbands.

31:15.483 --> 31:18.318
They all vowed to stand by me
for the rest of my life,

31:18.352 --> 31:20.019
but none of them did.

31:21.322 --> 31:23.156
Only one person
has always been there,

31:23.190 --> 31:26.025
for better or for worse.

31:26.059 --> 31:28.361
So I want you to have
this ring...

31:28.395 --> 31:30.580
not as a gift,

31:30.614 --> 31:33.399
but as my promise
to take care of you,

31:33.417 --> 31:36.569
just like you have always
taken care of me.

31:43.043 --> 31:45.094
But you still have to come up
with a plan.

31:45.129 --> 31:48.131
You have a lot of bills
coming in,

31:48.182 --> 31:50.383
and you can't keep
exchanging sex for watercolors.

31:50.417 --> 31:53.219
Oh, I have a plan.

31:53.253 --> 31:55.221
Uh-oh.

31:55.255 --> 31:56.606
What are you gonna do?

31:56.640 --> 31:59.091
What I've always done.

31:59.109 --> 32:02.145
It's time to find
husband number seven.

32:27.454 --> 32:29.556
You're right.

32:29.590 --> 32:31.624
I am jealous.

32:49.967 --> 32:51.834
Marisol, what are you doing up?

32:51.868 --> 32:54.971
I needed
to talk to you both.

32:55.005 --> 32:56.005
What's all this?

32:56.039 --> 32:57.757
I made Martinis.

32:57.808 --> 33:00.376
Thanks, but we're not thirsty.

33:00.394 --> 33:03.212
After I'm finished,

33:03.230 --> 33:06.098
you're going to want a drink.

33:09.903 --> 33:13.722
So how many of these DVDs
do you think Adrian has?

33:13.740 --> 33:17.276
Well, if Mr. Powell taped
one of your sessions,

33:17.327 --> 33:19.996
he probably taped all of them.

33:20.030 --> 33:21.730
Oh, my God.

33:21.748 --> 33:24.166
Obviously,
this could be devastating

33:24.201 --> 33:26.002
if any of these got out,

33:26.036 --> 33:27.736
landed on the Internet.

33:27.754 --> 33:28.737
Adrian wouldn't do that.

33:28.755 --> 33:30.339
Would he?

33:30.374 --> 33:33.909
He might not, but you probably
don't wanna take that chance.

33:33.927 --> 33:35.744
Now...

33:35.762 --> 33:38.881
