33:46.973 --> 33:50.443
Michael, did he ever
say anything to you?

33:52.312 --> 33:54.980
Mr. Stappord.

33:55.032 --> 33:56.866
Michael, where are you going?

33:58.869 --> 34:00.903
Oh, no.

34:11.297 --> 34:13.331
Michael. What a surprise.

34:13.382 --> 34:14.833
Did Evelyn let you in?

34:32.985 --> 34:34.136
The den.

34:41.745 --> 34:44.280
I bet you feel like
a big man now,

34:44.313 --> 34:45.498
which is ironic, considering...

34:45.532 --> 34:47.149
Where are they?

34:47.167 --> 34:48.951
Safe and sound.
Don't you worry.

34:48.985 --> 34:50.168
Uhh!

34:50.203 --> 34:51.420
Mr. Stappord, stop!

34:51.455 --> 34:52.838
You're gonna kill him!

34:52.873 --> 34:54.340
You listen to me, you pervert!

34:54.373 --> 34:57.126
I'm not leaving here
without those DVDs!

34:57.160 --> 34:58.594
Michael!

35:01.381 --> 35:04.183
Party's over. Get out.

35:07.020 --> 35:10.473
Perhaps my tone is not conveying
the seriousness of my intention.

35:14.010 --> 35:16.362
Have I made myself clear?

35:16.396 --> 35:17.897
Adrian has something
that belongs to me,

35:17.948 --> 35:19.565
and I'm not leaving
until I get it.

35:21.401 --> 35:23.852
Are you talking about the DVDs?

35:23.870 --> 35:25.204
You know?

35:25.238 --> 35:27.990
I know everything
that happens in this house.

35:28.024 --> 35:29.959
I'm going to give them
what they came for,

35:29.993 --> 35:32.027
and then we're gonna put this
nasty little mess behind us.

35:32.045 --> 35:33.963
Okay?

35:33.997 --> 35:35.498
Fine.

35:35.532 --> 35:38.250
I was tired
of looking at your wife anyway.

35:38.301 --> 35:40.202
So help me, Michael.

35:43.206 --> 35:45.541
Adrian?

35:45.559 --> 35:47.209
Go get some ice for your lip.

35:47.227 --> 35:50.312
Michael, you, Taylor, sit down.
Behave yourselves.

35:50.347 --> 35:52.064
I'm gonna get what you want.

35:52.098 --> 35:54.016
Marisol...

35:54.050 --> 35:56.569
come with me.

36:38.061 --> 36:39.862
Here we go.

36:47.487 --> 36:50.105
"The Taylor Collection"?

36:55.295 --> 36:57.379
As you can see,

36:57.414 --> 36:59.882
there are no other DVDs
bearing Taylor's name.

37:01.301 --> 37:04.303
Make sure you tell Michael
he has everything.

37:09.426 --> 37:12.928
Well, Michael, Taylor,

37:12.962 --> 37:16.015
obviously, we won't
be socializing anymore.

37:16.066 --> 37:17.299
What a relief it will be

37:17.317 --> 37:19.468
to stop pretending
that we like each other.

37:25.575 --> 37:26.992
Oh, and, Marisol?

37:29.279 --> 37:31.330
You're fired.

37:38.288 --> 37:41.090
Did you talk to the doctors?

37:41.124 --> 37:43.425
I did. Spence is doing
much better.

37:43.460 --> 37:45.344
He's awake and talking.

37:45.378 --> 37:47.429
Thank God.

37:49.332 --> 37:51.350
What is that?

37:51.384 --> 37:52.551
It's our wedding album.

37:52.602 --> 37:55.354
Just... got the urge
to go through it.

37:55.388 --> 37:58.190
Look.
It's Spence in his tux.

38:00.277 --> 38:01.477
So handsome.

38:01.511 --> 38:02.778
Wasn't he, though?

38:04.481 --> 38:07.733
You two seem very happy.

38:12.289 --> 38:15.624
I've decided
to go into therapy.

38:15.659 --> 38:17.543
Therapy?

38:17.577 --> 38:20.746
I want to understand why
I'm such a raging bitch.

38:22.165 --> 38:23.666
Ohh.

38:23.700 --> 38:26.635
You've seen me in action.
I'm a nightmare, right?

38:26.670 --> 38:28.170
No.

38:28.204 --> 38:29.638
I've seen worse.

38:29.673 --> 38:32.040
How? Did you clean
for Hitler?

38:32.058 --> 38:38.046
The things I say,
the way I act out...

38:38.064 --> 38:41.183
Something is wrong with me...

38:42.519 --> 38:45.521
And I'm going to fix it.

38:45.555 --> 38:49.057
What made you decide this?

38:51.444 --> 38:53.862
For the past year, I...

38:53.896 --> 38:56.448
began to think
I didn't love Spence anymore.

38:56.499 --> 39:01.587
But when
I saw him in that hospital...

39:01.621 --> 39:04.423
Oh, I do love him, Rosie.

39:04.457 --> 39:06.592
I just...

39:06.626 --> 39:08.677
forget it sometimes.

39:08.712 --> 39:11.513
Well...

39:11.548 --> 39:13.349
It's good you know that.

39:14.751 --> 39:16.635
So I'm gonna change for him,

39:16.686 --> 39:18.721
be the best wife ever.

39:18.755 --> 39:22.524
And Spence and I will
be happy again.

39:23.777 --> 39:26.145
It's a good thing,

39:26.196 --> 39:28.313
to be happy.

39:43.546 --> 39:44.613
Hello?

39:44.631 --> 39:47.299
Yeah, it's Michael.
I'm...

39:47.333 --> 39:50.085
I'm calling to see how you are.

39:50.119 --> 39:51.470
Well, apparently,

39:51.504 --> 39:53.422
I'm in need
of some plastic surgery.

39:53.456 --> 39:55.474
But to be fair,

39:55.508 --> 39:57.459
Evelyn's been saying that
for years.

39:57.477 --> 39:59.728
I had too much to drink.
You know how I get.

39:59.763 --> 40:02.264
I suppose I do.

40:02.298 --> 40:05.234
You know the real reason
why I came over there tonight,

40:05.268 --> 40:06.435
don't you, Adrian?

40:06.469 --> 40:09.571
You had an ulterior motive?
I'm shocked.

40:09.606 --> 40:12.107
I want that DVD back.

40:12.141 --> 40:13.642
The one with Flora?

40:13.660 --> 40:17.696
Relax. I smashed it
into a millions bits...

40:17.747 --> 40:19.281
a long time ago.

40:20.483 --> 40:22.150
Thank God.

40:22.168 --> 40:25.320
Obviously, back when I still
considered you a friend.

40:27.123 --> 40:29.658
Again, Adrian,
I'm sorry for what I did.

40:29.676 --> 40:32.177
Well, we all make mistakes.

